OL,3,CKings brings his 'greater together'
OL,4,Cmessage to New York
OL,6,FThe King and Queen concluded their
OL,7,Fvisit to New York with a glamorous
OL,8,Freception at Christie's, the British-
OL,9,Ffounded auction house.
OL,11,FCharles took his message promoting US-
OL,12,FUK links from the political corridors
OL,13,Fof DC, to a celebrity filled room in
OL,14,Fthe Big Apple.
OL,16,FHe was welcomed by Lionel Richie, who
OL,17,Fperformed in front of the King at
OL,18,FWindsor Castle following his
OL,19,Fcoronation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
