OL,3,CKings brings his 'greater together'
OL,4,Cmessage to New York
OL,6,FAs well as promoting British and
OL,7,FAmerican ties, the event also marked
OL,8,Fthe 50th anniversary of the King's
OL,9,FTrust, Charles' charity which supports
OL,10,Fyoung people launching their careers -
OL,11,Famong those it's helped, actor Idris
OL,12,FElba and fashion designer Ozwald
OL,13,FBoateng.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
