OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777521849
OL,3,CKings brings his 'greater together'
OL,4,Cmessage to New York
OL,6,F"I won't see the long-distance
OL,7,Ffuture," Charles said in a poignant
OL,8,Fmoment, "but I'm enormously grateful
OL,9,Fto you all for what you can all do as
OL,10,Fsupporters to help this vital
OL,11,Fendeavor, to champion the next
OL,12,Fgeneration, ensuring their talent and
OL,13,Fambition continue to strengthen our
OL,14,Fsocieties for many years to come."
OL,16,FThe King thanked Lionel Richie, and
OL,17,Fpraised his singing voice, joking, "I
OL,18,Fdon't know how he does it, he must
OL,19,Fgargle with port or something."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@bO]
