OL,3,CKings brings his 'greater together'
OL,4,Cmessage to New York
OL,6,FVogue Editor, Anna Wintour warmly
OL,7,Fgreeted the Queen.
OL,9,FOther celebrity guests included
OL,10,Ffashion designer Donatella Versace,
OL,11,Fbeauty entrepreneur Charlotte Tilbury
OL,12,Fand businesswoman Martha Stewart.
OL,14,FThe event aimed to showcase "the very
OL,15,Fbest of British-American philanthropy
OL,16,Fthrough the individual arts, culture,
OL,17,Finvestments between the two
OL,18,Fcountries," according to The King's
OL,19,FTrust USA CEO Victoria Gore.
OL,26,@vD@]OUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
