OL,3,CKings brings his 'greater together'
OL,4,Cmessage to New York
OL,6,FCharles noted the "wonderful
OL,7,Fopportunity" to celebrate "the
OL,8,Fenduring cultural bond" between the
OL,9,Ftwo countries, whose relationship he
OL,10,Fsaid is "rooted in shared creativity,
OL,11,Fenterprise and values. Reminding us we
OL,12,Fare truly greater together."
OL,14,FThe King and Queen returned to
OL,15,FWashington on Wednesday night, ahead
OL,16,Fof their final day in the US, when
OL,17,Fthey will return for one last time to
OL,18,Fthe White House.
