OL,3,CKings brings his 'greater together'
OL,4,Cmessage to New York
OL,6,FAfter saying goodbye to President
OL,7,FTrump and the First Lady the Royals
OL,8,Fwill head to Virginia to attend a
OL,9,F"block party" to celebrate America's
OL,10,F250th birthday.
OL,12,FThis will be their first opportunity
OL,13,Fto interact with the American public.
OL,15,FThe King will meet one of the area's
OL,16,Findigenous communities, in Shenandoah
OL,17,FNational Park, and people involved in
OL,18,Fconservation initiatives and efforts
OL,19,Fto protect America's natural
OL,20,Fenvironment.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@MO]
